high_descs: move forward across the bathroom to the green trash can

turn around and move across the bathroom to the left side of the toilet
put the sponge on the back lid of the toilet behind the pink bar of soap
move across the room towards the bath tub on the left side, turn to face the tub
pick up the sponge out of the bath tub
turn left and move across the room back to the left side of the toilet and turn to face the left side of the toilet
put the sponge on the back lid of the toilet to the right of the pink bar of soap
